I have tested this on Linux (Arch recent vintage) using GCC4.8 and OSX Mavericks (XCode 5.1 and bare Clang3.4).

The build requires a modern version of cmake (2.8 or later)

basic process - 

$ mkdir build && cd build
$ cmake ..
$ make install


To change the install location use -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX when invoking cmake
